abstract: Inbee Park and Yani Tseng share lead in HSBC Women’s Champions with six-under-par 66.
lead_paragraph: Inbee Park and Yani Tseng each shot a six-under-par 66 to share the lead after the opening round of the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore.

headline.main: Inbee Park and Yani Tseng Tie for Lead in Singapore
